description: Lola (overall 0-4) takes on Paris. Paris's only match previously was a thrashing by the Dragon. Lola ranked 10, needed to find some offence to handle the spirited Gemini. The Wild Child uses her experience and weight to good advantage as she outlasts the high energy Gemini. Lola gets her first dominating roll in RD 4 and puts it to her beaten opponent.
title: Gemini (0-1) vs. The Wild Child (0-1)
